Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The river is dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause everyone keeps throwing their trash in it. \NIt's like they're forgetting we've only got one Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.87,0:01:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You have smart thoughts, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just what someone on TV said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, let's go home to try mom's snacks. {g, no clue what's this oyasu}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:54.78,Sign,,0,0,90,,{\c&HBEB6AA&\bord5\blur5\3c&H496D00&\3a&H36&}Episode 86 \N{\fs30}Special Training with Personal Flovirtue-kun {じんとくんで特訓}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Korekiyo-kun! Today, we'll finally \Nsettle the scores in that game.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.56,0:02:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to games, I can't lose! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! They're throwing their litter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no helping those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you say something, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a problem with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't do. You gotta throw the cans \Ninto the specially designated bin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Empty cans can be reused too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta be frugal with the resources we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I did something good today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You ass! Since when do you think\Nyou can walk around telling me what to do?!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a busybody for the Environmental Agency?{}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You obnoxious worm!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, witness the\Ndeadly technique I devised myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao Special Number One!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Disgusting! \NJabao, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? \NWanna taste my deadly technique once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao Spe—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting is bad, Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was Jabao...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, Honmaru-kun \Nattacked me unprovoked!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's bullshit! Hey, Jabao!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! He was bullying us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Save us, Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not true! \NJabao and Korekiyo are the ones at fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao Special Number Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If Honmaru is speaking like that, \NI'm scared he might attack again, so please walk us home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't leave us to our fates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As a thank you, I've got some \Ndelicious soda for you back at home. {act. water but wtf}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's have a good time there, \Nall three of us!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They left, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! All I did was toss an empty can into the right bin—a supposedly good deed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, why do you say, \N"do good things and good things will return to you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Just like the sun and the Earth\Nare round, people are all big circles to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why good things that you do to others, \Ncome back to you after making a full circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And with bad deeds, they'll travel the circle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,coming back to you as even more bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Maru-chan, let's do lots of \Nood things and be happy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! You lied to me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How does doing good things \Nmake good things return to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I do good deeds, \NI only get the most horrible things in return!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done with good deeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mom, please say something at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A dead end. I can't even talk to mom about that...{}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:06:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat mama's snacks, Honmaru! It's yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of trying, even? {nc, tlc}{6:04: I'm hearing "俺ぐれちゃうかな"\Nhttps://jisho.org/word/%E3%81%90%E3%82%8C%E3%82%8B\NHe's wondering if he should become a delinquent.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tasty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, do you know what a personal virtue is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,People who have personal virtue are\Nliked by everyone, which is a good thing in itself.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That is also a good thing all around.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:27.62,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB486BB&\3c&H132046&\xshad-1\yshad4\4c&H0B5B6C&\4a&H48&\fs40}Personal virtue
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you build up your personal virtue, \Nlucky events will follow one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll also be popular with the girls, big time.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how do I build up that personal virtue?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then teach me how to do it, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, then. By performing many good deeds, \Nyou build up your personal virtue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to square one, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is mom trying to take me for a ride again?{h}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That personal virtue thing is a nonstarter for me. \NWhat's the point of good deeds?{}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru. Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Personal Flovirtue-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You sow the seeds of Flovirtue-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to know what Honmaru's personal virtue is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing on top of my head, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sprout up, sprout up, Flovirtue-kun. {/show shoots}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sprout up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! Taru, stop it, you! \NStop it, I said! Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If it sprouts up and the flower appears, \NHonmaru has personal virtue.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? The flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, it sprouted up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! And the flower bloomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That means I have personal virtue, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:08:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Have, have! Honmaru has personal virtue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still small, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, do you have personal virtue too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try it on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sprout up, sprout up, Flovirtue-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get your hopes too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't beat my gracious flower, that's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at my personal virtue flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's enormous compared to mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Taru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this, Honmaru? I beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Taru's personal virtue so huge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Why's that? Why? Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:09:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's because Taru-chan \Nis always working so hard for Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're heavy, Honmaru.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Taru-chan is such a good boy, \Nhis personal virtue is big.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, only good things \Nhave kept happening to Taru up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone likes him too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll build myself some big personal virtue too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come, life of good fortune and popularity!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just doing good things is enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I'll do all the dishes today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to Taru, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you watch! I'll grow myself an enormous flower too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good deed, good deed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, doing good things with a smile \Nis even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing things where no one\Ncan see you is also really good. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! Asking others \Nfor anything in return is a no-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, I did every single good\Nthing around I could think of. {}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You did plenty of good things, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, hurry up and sow the seeds of Flovirtue-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this? \NIt grew much bigger, didn't it, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how my fortuitous life starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Skip-skip, la-la-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope something good happens soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Honmaru-kun, Taru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know you can't skip in the hallway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, I appreciate your honest remorse.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful from now on, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, did you \Nunderstand the math class today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's alright. Come to the staff room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you more about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We also have delicious steamed buns there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:11:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:02.58,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB4AFC0&\fax0.1\3c&H100A1A&\pos(383.15,149.82)\fs40\frz349.9}Staff Room{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So good and tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, try some too, Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll nail the next math test.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so smart, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat as much as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he get steamed buns \Nfor being caught skipping in the hallway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher seems to be in a good mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we'll ride this train too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And... start!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Skip-skip, steamed buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat them sooner, steamed buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You two over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't skip in the hallway. Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, steamed buns are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tolerate you messing around.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you always have to be such a bad boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, I guess we got lucky, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to personal virtue, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ijigawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you want to meet me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being weird, Ijigawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I baked these cookies myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like it, you can eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Smells good cookie! Cookie!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ijigawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of lightning struck her? {chance; stroke of luck; (curious) turn of events}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because you're so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because you are wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally understood, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tickled pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you've been such a nice person lately, \Nboth Rui-chan and I couldn't help admiring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, you can have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Cookie! Cookie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like I can talk to Honmaru-kun \Nopenly about anything.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, leap straight into my arms. {/on my chest}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan admires me...{ore no koto}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cookie, cookie, lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, you're going home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome! Are you sure, Harako?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:14:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I prepared it specifically for you, no need to be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time we get there, \NI hope you enjoy yourselves thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I owe you one, Harako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, happy times are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Times are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that, Taru. \NWe can see our house from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Home looks small.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, of course it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I succeed in entertaining you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's superb!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Superb!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing that from you guys makes me happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, you truly are a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be my friend forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a token of my appreciation.{/my feeling}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad, though. Even getting a present for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what the present is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A wristwatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Harako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fluke! This is just what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Honmaru has personal virtue, everyone is kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have personal virtue, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no other student in our elementary school \Nwith quite as much personal virtue accumulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no, is no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Honmaru-kun. It's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, please accept this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine too!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,From that day on, my popularity and fortune \Nhave been steadily on the rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing good things daily...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...brought in return lucky days \Nwhere everything went as I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jabao-kun! Move outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? \NWho do you think you are, Honmaru?{}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Honmaru, the master of personal virtue.{/who has}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtueless and universally-hated people like you \Nshould keep it closer to the edges.{/stay further in the margins}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Move to the edges, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem with Honmaru-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna get even close to Jabao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Having such great personal virtue, \NI had no enemies wherever I'd go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have anything to fear either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid, splendid! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your subordination to me is now unquestionable. {g,tlc, 皆のもの苦しゅうないぞ *** }{https://jisho.org/word/%E8%8B%A6%E3%81%97%E3%82%85%E3%81%86%E3%81%AA%E3%81%84\NNot sure what to make of this line.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? Is that all \Nyou brought as a tribute today, Harako-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you? I wanted a super TV game and... \NHm... Let's make it a mountain bike. {was super famicom in manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is forgetting his place.{/messing with me}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're so rich, being stingy is a no-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it you who asked\Nme to remain as your friend forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do enough good things for others,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you may also accumulate personal virtue \Nand have good things happening to you, Harako-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fed up with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thou is a foolish kin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Some cakes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing to the foodstuffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope divine punishment hits you, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wasteful behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not my fault I'm so tired of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sup. What happened here? Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're wasting that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can eat it if you'd like to, Jabao-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk... If you're throwing it away, \Nat least throw it in the trash can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Korekiyo-kun, throw it away for me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can also accumulate personal virtue and have \Na life of good things if you do enough good things for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Iyona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you get for flying too high, Honmaru. {hope she means "getting carried away"}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? You're sickening me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, that's indecent! {/pervert}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Still no divine punishment! {nc, kinda hear batsu?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even divine punishment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,won't be enough! {/unforgivable}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The world doesn't revolve around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you decide what I deserve or not?! {/what is unforgivable}\NDid you forget who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Honmaru-sama himself! \NRight, Iyona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-ch—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand this side of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! But, wait... I'm the king of personal virtue!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, my personal virtue flower is enormous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough saying nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Personal Flovirtue-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now sow the seeds quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a huge flower, I'll show you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My personal virtue is extraordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, please hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be too surprised when you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sprout up, sprout up, Flovirtue-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you starting to wake up to my greatness?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My flower...{}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is rotting!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Please wait! Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Iyona! Faster!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, they're all done for. {assuming he means flowers, tho not sure it's even shinuzo}\NThat flower is rotting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,From getting carried away,\Nyou lost all your personal virtue!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.42,0:21:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone going to hate me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:21:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, if you work hard again, doing good things,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful flowers will bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, this time, you'll become \Na good guy for real. I believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru... Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.25,0:22:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come close, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.37,0:22:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! I'm on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.36,0:22:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Me on fire too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The main event of the cherry blossom viewing \Nis the big obstacle race. Iyona-chan's lips will be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru drooling. Drooling!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm excited to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:22:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:22:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But remember, magic is forbidden, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.59,0:22:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:22:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only kiss the takoyaki! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Taruruuto-kun: \NThe Most Important Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.86,0:23:02.86,Sign,,0,0,0,,Episode 87 \NThe Most Important Kiss ❤ {一番大事なキッス}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on fire-ru-ru!
